<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="113" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="2.[166,1225,436,1839]" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">
D i a g n o s i s. Species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Coquillett" authorityYear="1898" box="[525,644,437,462]" class="Insecta" family="Pyrgotidae" genus="Eupyrgota" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="113" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[525,644,437,462]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">Eupyrgota</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
can be recognized from the other Old World Pyrgotini by the following combination of characters: prosternum bearing a pair of nipple- or finger-like lobes, femora apico-ventrally with postero- and antero-ventral row of thickened setae (
<figureCitation box="[362,422,532,559]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="11.[174,207,1680,1702]" captionTargetBox="[226,1185,174,1660]" captionTargetId="figure-5@11.[226,1188,174,1676]" captionTargetPageId="11" captionText="Fig. 5. Eupyrgota brahma, holotype ♀ Adapsilia brahma (BMNH) (1–2) and holotype ♀ Adapsilia nocturna (BMNH) (3–9): 1, 3 — habitus, dorsal; 5 — same, left; 2, 4 — labels; 6–7 — head (3 — anterior left view; 4 — dorsal); 8 — wing; 9 — abdomen, dorsally. Рис. 5. Eupyrgota brahma, голотип ♀ Adapsilia brahma (BMNH) (1–2) и голотип ♀ Adapsilia nocturna (BMNH) (3–9): 1, 3 — общий вид, дорсально; 5 — same, слева; 2, 4 — этикетки; 6–7 — голова (3 — спереди слева view; 4 — дорсально); 8 — крыло; 9 — брюшко,дорсально." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6403941" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6403941/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">fig. 5</figureCitation>
, 
<emphasis box="[435,477,532,559]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">
<figureCitation box="[435,451,532,558]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="12.[166,199,1666,1688]" captionTargetBox="[220,1195,215,1565]" captionTargetId="figure-8@12.[188,1210,206,1590]" captionTargetPageId="12" captionText="Fig. 6. Eupyrgota nyambene, sp. n., holotype ♀ (NMKE): 1 — habitus, left; 2–5 — head (2 — anterior left; 3 — anterior; 4 — left; 5 — dorsal); 6 — fore femur, posterior view; 7 — mid femur, anterior; 8 — wing; 9 — abdomen, ventral. Рис. 6. Eupyrgota nyambene, sp. n., голотип ♀ (NMKE): 1 — общий вид, слева; 2–5 — голова (2 — спереди слева;3 — спереди; 4 — слева;5 — дорсально); 6 — переднее бедро,вид сзади;7 — среднее бедро, спереди; 8 — крыло; 9 — брюшко, вентрально." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6403943" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6403943/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">6</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[463,477,533,559]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="14.[166,199,1721,1743]" captionTargetBox="[190,1222,602,1675]" captionTargetId="figure-128@14.[166,1231,602,1679]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="Fig. 7. Eupyrgota vespiformis, ♀ (NMKE): 1 — habitus, left; 2–4 — head (2 — anterior left; 3 — left anterior; 4 — dorsal); 5 — wing; 6–7 — abdomen (6 — left; 7— dorsal)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6403947" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6403947/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">7</figureCitation>
</emphasis>
; 
<figureCitation box="[491,506,533,559]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="16.[166,199,1588,1610]" captionTargetBox="[241,1189,195,1506]" captionTargetId="figure-8@16.[240,1189,195,1510]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="Fig. 8. Eupyrgota flaviseta, holotype ♀ (1–6), paratypes ♀ (7–9) and} (10–14) (USNM): 1 — habitus, left; 2 — labels; 3–4 — head (3 — left; 4 — dorsal); 5 — fore femur and tibia, posterior view; 6 — mid femur, anterior view; 7 — epandrium, right; 8–9 — phallus glans, right and ventral; 10 — abdomen, dorsal; 11 — same, ventral, macerated in KOH; 12 — oviscape apex, ventrally; 13 — aculeus, ventral; 14 — spermathecae." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6403949" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6403949/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">8</figureCitation>
, 
<emphasis box="[519,561,532,559]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">
<figureCitation box="[519,535,533,559]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="11.[174,207,1680,1702]" captionTargetBox="[226,1185,174,1660]" captionTargetId="figure-5@11.[226,1188,174,1676]" captionTargetPageId="11" captionText="Fig. 5. Eupyrgota brahma, holotype ♀ Adapsilia brahma (BMNH) (1–2) and holotype ♀ Adapsilia nocturna (BMNH) (3–9): 1, 3 — habitus, dorsal; 5 — same, left; 2, 4 — labels; 6–7 — head (3 — anterior left view; 4 — dorsal); 8 — wing; 9 — abdomen, dorsally. Рис. 5. Eupyrgota brahma, голотип ♀ Adapsilia brahma (BMNH) (1–2) и голотип ♀ Adapsilia nocturna (BMNH) (3–9): 1, 3 — общий вид, дорсально; 5 — same, слева; 2, 4 — этикетки; 6–7 — голова (3 — спереди слева view; 4 — дорсально); 8 — крыло; 9 — брюшко,дорсально." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6403941" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6403941/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">5</figureCitation>
