<figureCitation box="[1160,1220,564,591]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="6.[166,199,1357,1379]" captionTargetBox="[196,1203,181,1342]" captionTargetId="figure-176@6.[196,1203,174,1356]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="Fig.2. Eupyrgota alienata, holotype ♀ (BMNH) (1–2) and non-type ♀ (NHMB) (3–6): 1 — habitus, dorsal; 2 — labels; 3–4 — head (3 — left; 4 — anterior); 5 — wing; 6 — fore coxa. Рис. 2. Eupyrgota alienata, голотип ♀ (BMNH) (1–2) и нетиповая ♀ (NHMB) (3–6): 1 — общий вид, дорсально; 2 — этикетки; 3–4 — голова (3 — слева; 4 — спереди); 5 — крыло; 6 — передний тазик." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6403935" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6403935/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">fig. 2</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[166,180,597,623]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="9.[174,207,1641,1663]" captionTargetBox="[263,1145,180,1601]" captionTargetId="figure-5@9.[191,1208,174,1626]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="Fig. 4. Eupyrgota armipes, holotype ♀ (BMNH): 1 — habitus, left; 2 — labels; 3–5 — head (3 — left; 4 — anterior; 5 — dorsal); 6 — fore femur and tibia, posterior view; 7 — mid femur, anterior view; 8 — fore trochanter; 9 — mid trochanter; 10 — wing; 11 — mesonotum and abdomen, dorsally; 12 — abdomen, posterior." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6403939" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6403939/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">
